          "description": "As a member of the Android Mobile App team, I worked to enhance the design of the app's user interface, create AB tests, and fix bugs. I collaborated and worked with the design, database, and iOS teams throughout all stages of the development life cycle of a product. I had the opportunity to work on both internal projects to improve the efficiency of the software engineers and also stories for the android main Expedia app that also impacted several of Expedia Inc's companies such as Hotwire and Travelocity. \nI am most proud of creating a feature Bug Reporter, which is a android library easily implemented within any android mobile development team. It makes the bug reporting process much more efficient for software engineers by allowing the user to find, report, and identify the cause of a bug. Bug reporter is designed to detect a user shaking the device, which in turn creates a screenshot that can be annotated and then automatically sent within an email app on the android test device attaching device information, the annotated screenshot, and a log file. Bug Reporter is now actively and successfully being used within Expedia.",
